---
// Hero.astro â€” Desk photo embedded as base64
import Button from '../atoms/Button.astro';
import { company, heroStats } from '../../data/company';

const DESK_B64 = "data:image/jpeg;base64,";
---

<section
  id="hero"
  class="relative min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-center
         pt-[130px] pb-[120px] px-[4vw] overflow-hidden"
  aria-label="Hero"
>
  <!-- Desk photo background â€” embedded, no file needed -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center opacity-10 scale-105"
    style={`background-image: url('${DESK_B64}');`}
    role="presentation"
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>

  <!-- Gradient overlays -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-hero-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gold-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <!-- Geometric decoration -->
  <div class="absolute right-[7vw] top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[340px] h-[340px] opacity-15 pointer-events-none hidden xl:block" aria-hidden="true">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 340 340" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <circle cx="170" cy="170" r="160" stroke="#c8a44a" stroke-width="0.5"/>
      <circle cx="170" cy="170" r="115" stroke="#c8a44a" stroke-width="0.5"/>
      <circle cx="170" cy="170" r="70"  stroke="#c8a44a" stroke-width="0.5"/>
      <line x1="170" y1="10"  x2="170" y2="330" stroke="#c8a44a" stroke-width="0.5"/>
      <line x1="10"  y1="170" x2="330" y2="170" stroke="#c8a44a" stroke-width="0.5"/>
      <line x1="57"  y1="57"  x2="283" y2="283" stroke="#c8a44a" stroke-width="0.5"/>
      <line x1="283" y1="57"  x2="57"  y2="283" stroke="#c8a44a" stroke-width="0.5"/>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <!-- Main content -->
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-[800px]">
    <p class="text-eyebrow flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
      <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-gold animate-pulse" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      {company.type} Â· {company.location} Â· {company.country}
    </p>

    <h1 class="font-display text-display-xl font-light text-ivory leading-[1.05] mb-8">
      {company.heroLine1}<br />
      {company.heroLine2}<br />
      <em class="text-gold-500 not-italic">{company.heroLine3}</em>
    </h1>

    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-10">
      <div class="w-10 h-px bg-gold" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <p class="text-eyebrow tracking-[0.25em]">
        {company.tagWords.join(' Â· ')}
      </p>
    </div>

    <p class="text-body-lg text-silver max-w-[540px] mb-12 leading-[1.9]">
      {company.heroDescription}
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
      <Button href="#contact" variant="primary">Engage With Us â†’</Button>
      <Button href="#about" variant="ghost">Our Story</Button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Stats panel -->
  <div
    class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 left-0
           lg:left-auto lg:right-[4vw] lg:bottom-[4vw]
           bg-charcoal/90 backdrop-blur-md border-t border-gold/20
           lg:border border-gold/20
           grid grid-cols-3 lg:flex lg:gap-0
           lg:max-w-fit"
    aria-label="Key statistics"
  >
    {heroStats.map((stat, i) => (
      <div
        class={[
          'flex flex-col items-center lg:items-start justify-center',
          'px-6 py-5 lg:px-10 lg:py-6',
          i < heroStats.length - 1 ? 'border-r border-gold/15' : ''
        ].join(' ')}
      >
        <span class="font-display text-[1.6rem] lg:text-[2rem] text-gold font-light">
          {stat.value}
        </span>
        <span class="text-[0.6rem] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-silver/60 mt-1">
          {stat.label}
        </span>
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>
</section>
